postNum8.image-text: My son Finn’s closest friend and training partner during his years as a competitive Big Air skiier is #ColbyStevenson. Watch this moving film of Colby’s recovery from a devastating head injury. Today Colby will compete in the X games in Aspen which he dominated last year winning two gold medals. He was the first rookie to score first place in Slopestyle He skis at 10:00 PST in the Slopestyle (Big Air) competition and around 8:00 pm in the breathtaking evening Knucklehuck Jump. Tune in for the excitement and to root for this extraordinarly courageous and inspiring young man.
